Dia dah pergikah?

324
00:35:14,620 --> 00:35:17,220
Saya tak rasa dia akan putus asa lagi.

325
00:35:17,720 --> 00:35:19,700
Dia tertidur di atas katil awak.

326
00:35:19,870 --> 00:35:23,100
