543
00:51:29,760 --> 00:51:32,400
dia nampak seorang lelaki
pakai uniform berdarah.

544
00:51:32,490 --> 00:51:33,700
Bukan dia saja.

545
00:51:33,790 --> 00:51:36,010
Gi-yeong yang mati di Lembah Eorae

546
00:51:36,100 --> 00:51:39,460
